<main>
  <div class="hero">
    <div class="shadow_overlay"></div>
    <header id="pageHeader">
      <div class="row top">
        <div class="columns logo">
          <a href="/"><%= image_tag "landing/logo-white.png", alt: "Airbo" %></a>
        </div>
        <div class="columns headerMenu">
          <ul>
            <li><%= link_to "Home", "" %></li>
            <li><%= link_to "Company", "#!", class: "company_link" %></li>
            <li><%= link_to "Blog", "http://blog.airbo.com", target: "_blank" %></li>
            <li><%= link_to "Sign in", sign_in_path %></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>
    <div class="hero_section">
      <div class="hero_content">
        <h1>Software for HR to create engaging employee programs & communications in minutes</h1>
        <%= link_to "Request Demo", "", class: "request_demo" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="clients">
    <div class="clients_section row">
      <h5>Airbo customers range from 20 to 65,000 employee companies across every industry.</h5>
      <div class="client_logos">
        <div class="small-4 columns">
          <%= image_tag "landing/Fujifilm-logo.png" %>
        </div>
        <div class="small-4 columns">
          <%= image_tag "landing/asha-logo.png" %>
        </div>
        <div class="small-4 columns">
          <%= image_tag "landing/milton-cat-logo.png" %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="money">
    <div class="money_section row">
      <h2>
        Airbo helps HR get more programs done faster, for less, and with higher participation.
      </h2>
      <%= image_tag "landing/mac-full.png" %>
      <div class="benefits_group">
        <div class="small-4 columns">
          <div class="benefit_block">
            <div class="title">Easy Content Creation</div>
            <div class="desc">
              Pick a priority you want to accomplish and instantly receive best practice content. You can customize it for your company, or, create your own content in minutes.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="small-4 columns">
          <div class="benefit_block">
            <div class="title">More Participation</div>
            <div class="desc">
              Content is delivered to employees in a fun and interactive format that feels like a consumer tool. Airbo works on computers, phones and tablets.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="small-4 columns">
          <div class="benefit_block">
            <div class="title">Less Administration</div>
            <div class="desc">
              Airbo automatically drives participation and tracks engagement, which means less administration, follow-ups, and employee questions.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="try">
    <div class="shadow_overlay"></div>
    <div class="try_section">
      <h2>Try Airbo</h2>
      <p>
        "Health plan basics" board helps demonstrate how Airbo can be used to help teach employees the basics of health insurance in 15 minutes. Created by Airbo with data sourced from healthcare.gov and Kaiser Family Foundation.
      </p>
      <%= link_to "Try This Board Out", "#" %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="case_study">
    <div class="case_study_section row">
      <h2>Case study</h2>
      <div class="quote">
        "Airbo is easy for me and engaging for everyone"
      </div>
      <div class="user">
        <div class="image columns">
          <%= image_tag "landing/userpic.png" %>
        </div>
        <div class="name columns">
          - Janet McNichol, Director of HR at The American Speech–Language–Hearing Association
        </div>
      </div>
      <%= link_to "Read This Case Study", "#" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>
<footer id="pageFtr">
  <div class="row page_footer_section">
    <div class="menu_block columns large-6">
      <ul class="ftrMenu">
        <li><%= link_to "Home", "" %></li>
        <li><%= link_to "Company", "#!", class: "company_link" %></li>
        <li><%= link_to "Blog", "http://blog.airbo.com", target: "_blank" %></li>
        <li><%= link_to "Sign in", sign_in_path %></li>
        <li><%= link_to "Request Demo", "#!", class: "request_demo_link" %></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="columns large-6 contacts_block">
      <a href="/"><%= image_tag "landing/logo-blue.png", alt: "Airbo" %></a>
      <div class="contacts">
        <span>
          Contact Sales:
        </span>
        <span>
          (866) 247-2632
        </span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
